data.description: ASSUMABLE VA Loan if eligible!! Welcome to your new home! This is a spacious 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence boasts an array of desirable features and a prime location between Austin & San Antonio, shopping and Retama Park. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an inviting layout highlighted by an office space, perfect for remote work or creative endeavors. The granite kitchen counters add a touch of elegance to the heart of the home, while the garden tub in the master bathroom offers a tranquil retreat after a long day. Entertain with ease in the generously-sized game room, ideal for game time and movies. Step outside to discover the covered patio, where you can enjoy outdoor dining and relaxation amidst the beautifully landscaped yard and serene green belt views.    This home is equipped with modern amenities including solar screens, a smart thermostat, and a water softener to provide efficiency. The irrigation system ensures lush greenery year-round.  Don't miss the opportunity to experience comfortable living combined with unparalleled convenience. Schedule your showing today and make this remarkable home your own!
